member.summary:
This constructor check if a mod is Here or is Enabled.

            Example of call :

                var RocketLib_info = new IsThisModIs("RocketLib");

This constructor check if a mod is Here or is Enabled. Actually it don't work.

            Example of call :

                RocketLib.IsThisModIs RocketLib_info = new RocketLib.IsThisModIs("RocketLib");

member.example:
We have 2 classes

class A
{
    B b;
}
class B
{
    int number = 8;
}

If we want to get 'B.Number' from A,  should be 'b.number'

